{"id":250858,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-江苏响水县化工企业屡屡爆炸威胁民众生/","date":"2012-09-09T12:46:26Z","modified":"2012-09-09T12:46:26Z","title":"维权网 | 江苏响水县化工企业屡屡爆炸威胁民众生命财产安全（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员钟剑报道）江苏省响水县多年来急功近利，引进大批高耗能、高污染的化工企业，建立“陈家港镇化工集中区”，紧邻居民区、养蜂场。不仅造成严重的环境污染，还直接威胁附近居民的生命财产安全。　　　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2007</span><span>年“联化化工厂”的大爆炸，造成多人死亡；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2010</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月初“正翔硅业化工厂”的贮罐燃烧爆炸，大量三氯氢硅经燃烧所释放的二氧化硅、氯气、氯化氢，造成几十人伤残，蜂场死蜂遍地，惨不忍睹（附照片）。养蜂人交涉半年，才得到部分补偿。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aqSvysKFp4k/UExDDhanUsI/AAAAAAAANuM/QiOvfY2YgXg/s1600/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83_middle.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"262\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-aqSvysKFp4k/UExDDhanUsI/AAAAAAAANuM/QiOvfY2YgXg/s320/%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83_middle.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2011</span><span>年再次发生毒气泄漏，造成了网络闻名的“江苏响水县万人大逃亡”。爆炸造成养蜂人邵中华苦心经营十多年、价值二十多万元的养蜂场被彻底摧毁，全家人的生活来源也断了，整天生存在担心恐慌中。　　　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>维权网信息员了解到，经过长期的维权努力，去年底养蜂人邵中华获得了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>万元的赔偿，但是这与实际损失差距太大。因此，邵中华准备</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>大期间到北京上访，坚决要求：赔偿蜂场的全部经济损失；化工厂立即停产，归还绿色家园！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>单纯追求经济效益，不顾及环境的保护及造成的污染治理，其结果不仅导致环境恶化，更使公民的财产权、生命权得不到保障。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>　　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>联系联系人：养蜂人</span><span> </span><span>邵中华</span><span> </span><span>孙国霞</span><span> </span><span>邵林谱</span><span> </span><span>邵凤玲</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>联系电话：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">0515&#8211;86734933 </span><span>手机：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13770191289</span></div>\n<div><span>地址：江苏省盐城市响水县陈家港镇响陈路边王商牌</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-2885984460235309956?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}